thread.title: Jason Davis
thread.title_full: TShirt Studio reviewed by Jason Davis

author: Jason Davis
title: Jason Davis
text: Print quality on t-shirts and hoodies was excellent, as was their customer service. Went out of their way to make sure the design was right, even suggesting changes that could be made to the original design. Great quality, speedy delivery and a good company to deal with. Highly recommended.
